Play around with the co-variates used in [Recursive Partitioning](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Recursive_partitioning) and see the results updated below.  The underlying analysis is performed using the [R](https://www.r-project.org/) package [rpart](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/rpart/) and it is recommended you read the packages [vignette](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/rpart/vignettes/glmnet\_beta.html), in particular the section on logistic regression.
